BR Malls Stores Sales Rose 24 Percent in the Third Quarter

-- B y   F a b i o l a   M o u r a
-- 
2011-10-18T21:36:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/br-malls-stores-sales-rose-24-percent-in-the-third-quarter.html
BR Malls Participacoes SA (BRML3)  said sales
in stores located in the shopping malls it operates rose 24
percent to 3.9 billion reais in the third quarter, according to
preliminary results sent in a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabiola Moura in New York at 
 fdemoura@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jose Sergio Osse at 
